description: In a room behind a door, a young woman named Sylvie adventures through the depths of her own heart. She builds a world that can keep her safe from all of the "what if's" she fears most, never daring to venture beyond the threshold of her door. But soon, many visitors begin coming to her doorLove, Joy, Self Pity and Apathy. Some of these visitors hope to embolden Sylvie to step beyond, others seek to keep her stuck indefinitely. And there is another visitor who Sylvie knows from her dreams, a kind man named Jesus who has many truths to teach Sylvie along the way. The Girl Behind the Door is a journey you won't soon forget.
